11#ifndef MODULES_CONGESTION_CONTROLLER_INCLUDE_RECEIVE_SIDE_CONGESTION_CONTROLLER_H_
12#define MODULES_CONGESTION_CONTROLLER_INCLUDE_RECEIVE_SIDE_CONGESTION_CONTROLLER_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15#include <vector>
16
17#include "api/transport/field_trial_based_config.h"
18#include "api/transport/network_control.h"
19#include "api/units/data_rate.h"
20#include "modules/congestion_controller/remb_throttler.h"
21#include "modules/include/module.h"
22#include "modules/pacing/packet_router.h"
23#include "modules/remote_bitrate_estimator/remote_estimator_proxy.h"
24#include "rtc_base/synchronization/mutex.h"
25
26namespace webrtc {
27class RemoteBitrateEstimator;
28class RemoteBitrateObserver;
29
30// This class represents the congestion control state for receive
31// streams. For send side bandwidth estimation, this is simply
32// relaying for each received RTP packet back to the sender. While for
33// receive side bandwidth estimation, we do the estimation locally and
34// send our results back to the sender.
35class ReceiveSideCongestionController : public CallStatsObserver,
36 public Module {
37 public:
38 ReceiveSideCongestionController(
39 Clock* clock,
40 RemoteEstimatorProxy::TransportFeedbackSender feedback_sender,
41 RembThrottler::RembSender remb_sender,
42 NetworkStateEstimator* network_state_estimator);
43
44 ~ReceiveSideCongestionController() override {}
45
46 virtual void OnReceivedPacket(int64_t arrival_time_ms,
47 size_t payload_size,
48 const RTPHeader& header);
49
50 void SetSendPeriodicFeedback(bool send_periodic_feedback);
51 // TODO(nisse): Delete these methods, design a more specific interface.
52 virtual RemoteBitrateEstimator* GetRemoteBitrateEstimator(bool send_side_bwe);
53 virtual const RemoteBitrateEstimator* GetRemoteBitrateEstimator(
54 bool send_side_bwe) const;
55
56 // Implements CallStatsObserver.
57 void OnRttUpdate(int64_t avg_rtt_ms, int64_t max_rtt_ms) override;
58
59 // This is send bitrate, used to control the rate of feedback messages.
60 void OnBitrateChanged(int bitrate_bps);
61
62 // Ensures the remote party is notified of the receive bitrate no larger than
63 // |bitrate| using RTCP REMB.
64 void SetMaxDesiredReceiveBitrate(DataRate bitrate);
65
66 // Implements Module.
67 int64_t TimeUntilNextProcess() override;
68 void Process() override;
69
70 private:
71 class WrappingBitrateEstimator : public RemoteBitrateEstimator {
72 public:
73 WrappingBitrateEstimator(RemoteBitrateObserver* observer, Clock* clock);
74
75 WrappingBitrateEstimator() = delete;
76 WrappingBitrateEstimator(const WrappingBitrateEstimator&) = delete;
77 WrappingBitrateEstimator& operator=(const WrappingBitrateEstimator&) =
78 delete;
79
80 ~WrappingBitrateEstimator() override;
81
82 void IncomingPacket(int64_t arrival_time_ms,
83 size_t payload_size,
84 const RTPHeader& header) override;
85
86 void Process() override;
87
88 int64_t TimeUntilNextProcess() override;
89
90 void OnRttUpdate(int64_t avg_rtt_ms, int64_t max_rtt_ms) override;
91
92 void RemoveStream(unsigned int ssrc) override;
93
94 bool LatestEstimate(std::vector<unsigned int>* ssrcs,
95 unsigned int* bitrate_bps) const override;
96
97 void SetMinBitrate(int min_bitrate_bps) override;
98
99 private:
100 void PickEstimatorFromHeader(const RTPHeader& header)
101 RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(mutex_);
102 void PickEstimator() RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(mutex_);
103 RemoteBitrateObserver* observer_;
104 Clock* const clock_;
105 mutable Mutex mutex_;
106 std::unique_ptr<RemoteBitrateEstimator> rbe_;
107 bool using_absolute_send_time_;
108 uint32_t packets_since_absolute_send_time_;
109 int min_bitrate_bps_;
110 };
111
112 const FieldTrialBasedConfig field_trial_config_;
113 RembThrottler remb_throttler_;
114 WrappingBitrateEstimator remote_bitrate_estimator_;
115 RemoteEstimatorProxy remote_estimator_proxy_;
116};
117
118} // namespace webrtc
119
120#endif // MODULES_CONGESTION_CONTROLLER_INCLUDE_RECEIVE_SIDE_CONGESTION_CONTROLLER_H_
